ureTheory/Function/AbsolutelyContinuous.html#AbsolutelyContinuousOnInterval.disjWithin\">disjWithin</a> <span class=\"fn\">a</span> <span class=\"fn\">b</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hi</span> : <span class=\"fn\">i</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LT.lt\">&lt;</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Interval/Set/UnorderedInterval.html#Set.uIoc\">Set.uIoc</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">I</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span>)</span>.1</span> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">I</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span>)</span>.2</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#HasSubset.Subset\">⊆</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Interval/Set/UnorderedInterval.html#Set.uIoc\">Set.uIoc</a> <span class=\"fn\">a</span> <span class=\"fn\">b</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/MeasureTheory/Function/AbsolutelyContinuous.html#AbsolutelyContinuousOnInterval.uIoc_subset_of_mem_disjWithin","kind":"theorem","line":103,"name":"AbsolutelyContinuousOnInterval.uIoc_subset_of_mem_disjWithin","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/MeasureTheory/Function/AbsolutelyContinuous.lean#L103-L109"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/MeasureTheory/Function/AbsolutelyContinuous.html#AbsolutelyContinuousOnInterval.disjWithin_mono\"><span class=\"name\">AbsolutelyContinuousOnInterval</span>.<span class=\"name\">disjWithin_mono</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class